      <title>What freedom means to NPR readers. And, the secret to a perfect July 4 pasta salad</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/07/04/g-s1-75658/independence-day-freedom-meaning</link>
      <comments>https://text.npr.org/2025/07/04/g-s1-75658/independence-day-freedom-meaning</comments>
